    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age both mechanically and cosmetically. The exterior has some noticeable scratches, minor dings, and fading clear coat in a few spots, while the interior shows typical wear on the upholstery and carpets. Mechanically, the car runs and shifts through all gears, but it will soon require routine maintenance such as new tires and a brake service. It is a solid, honest car for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a bit of character and some upcoming weekend projects.",
