    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. This specimen has been curated for the driver who values both performance and reliability. Meticulously maintained and showing minimal signs of previous ownership, it offers a refined driving experience. We invite you to experience the caliber of this exceptional motorcar firsthand.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been truly loved? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and let me tell you, it\u2019s been a total dream to drive. It\u2019s in great shape and has so much life left for all your upcoming road trips and daily commutes! It\u2019s clean, runs smoothly, and is just waiting for a new owner to take the wheel. Come take it for a spin\u2014I promise you\u2019re going to love how it feels on the road!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and a VANOS system overhaul. The suspension geometry remains true with refreshed control arm bushings and Bilstein dampers. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals are robust, offering linear power delivery and precise turn-in for the discerning specialist.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Reliable performance. Maintenance records available. Clean interior. No accidents.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-loved and meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily reliability. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front bumper\u2014honest wear from highway commutes. Inside, the cabin remains a serene environment; the leather seats are supple with only light creasing on the driver's bolster, and all electronics, from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control, function perfectly. Mechanically, this car is sound, having received consistent synthetic oil changes and a recent full brake service. It drives straight and true, with a responsive engine and a transmission that shifts smoothly through every gear. If you are looking for a dependable, high-quality ride that has been cared for by a responsible owner, this is the one.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies both performance and reliability. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. Featuring a refined interior and a robust powertrain, it offers an exceptional driving experience for the discerning professional. We invite you to experience the superior value and uncompromising quality that define our curated inventory.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting or headed out on a weekend road trip, this car is ready to go! It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and has been well-loved. I'd love to see it go to a great new home where it'll be appreciated just as much as I have. Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This FD3S-generation RX-7 is a prime example of 90s JDM engineering, featuring the iconic 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine. The powerplant delivers a smooth, high-revving power band, managed by a factory 5-speed manual gearbox and a Torsen limited-slip differential. The chassis retains its legendary 50/50 weight distribution and aluminum double-wishbone suspension, offering precise turn-in and exceptional mechanical grip. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive vacuum line 'rat's nest' refresh to ensure optimal boost transition between the primary and secondary Hitachi HT12 turbos. While the paint exhibits minor road wear, the structural integrity and drivetrain performance remain robust, with healthy compression across all rotor faces. A mechanically sound driver's car for the serious enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
